<!--<h4><hi rend="italic">First Face.</hi></h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śakavarṣaṁbulu 1043 gu śrāhi svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> samasta
<lb n="2" break="no"/>bhuvanāśraya śrīpridhvīvallabha mahārājādhirāja
<lb n="3"/>paramēsvara paramabhaṭṭāraka satyāśrayakulatilaka
<lb n="4"/>cā<supplied reason="omitted">lu</supplied>kyābharana śrīma<unclear>ttri</unclear>bhuvanamalladēvara vijayarā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>jyamuttarōttarābhivriddhipravarddhamānamācaṁdrārkka
<lb n="6" break="no"/>tārakaṁ cirasthāyigā śrīmaccālukyavikramasaṁva
<lb n="7" break="no"/>tsa 46 gu śrāhi guddavādināṁṭṭi peddaḍākarēmi śrī
<lb n="8" break="no"/>bhīmēsvaramahādēvaraku pōlunāṇṭi Āriya
<lb n="9"/>vaṭṭanamuna satterāju tana <unclear>dha</unclear>rmārtthamugānu śrībhī
<lb n="10" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<!--<h4><hi rend="italic">Second Face.</hi></h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="11"/>satterāju tanavrittiyaina Ariyavaṭṭanamuna viḍci
<lb n="12" break="no"/>na Ūḍvunēla Ēḍu vuṭlakuṁ jatussīmamulu prama
<lb n="13" break="no"/>laĀvakuṁ durppuna Alamu sīmamu dakṣinamu mā
<lb n="14" break="no"/>viṇḍivāḍa polagarusa sīmamu nairatimula ce[<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> ṛvu]
<lb n="15"/>lōpugāṁ baḍumaṭa garuva sīmamu Uttaramuna
<lb n="16"/>ceṟvunaku Iśānamuna ceṟvu lōpugā E<unclear>ṟa</unclear>sīma
<lb n="17" break="no"/>mu <unclear>yī</unclear> pannasa ceḍi kāṁppulaku yī bhūmi tama
<lb n="18"/><unclear>ga</unclear>ruvuna viḍci yilupaṭla nēla paṁdumulōpugā
<lb n="19" break="no"/>nu sarvvakaraparihāramugāviḍsi śilāsāsanamu ve
<lb n="20" break="no"/>ṭṭiṁciri <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> likitaṁ peddanāsari <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> yisthala dharmmuvu
<lb n="21"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ceṟcirēni gaṁggaka<unclear>ṛta</unclear> kavulala poḍcinavā<unclear>ru</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

